{
  "_comment": "VST2 FXP layout from vst2-preset-parser (big-endian). Cross-ref: CharlesHolbrow/vst2-preset-parser, Steinberg Vst2xProgram. Chunk (FPCh) payload is plugin-specific; only header validated here.",
  "header": [
